Package: fin452golem
Title: Energy Commodity Risk Management Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Alex", "Hirtle", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alex@example.com")
Description: A Golem-based Shiny dashboard for senior energy commodity risk managers.
    Covers WTI (CL, HTT), Brent (BRN), Heating Oil (HO), RBOB Gasoline, and Natural Gas (NG)
    futures markets traded on the CME. Features forward curve analysis, volatility analytics,
    co-dynamics, seasonality, and hedge ratio tracking.
